<% include ./include/head %>
<% include ./include/musicnotation %>
<body>
  <% include ./include/nav %>
  <main class="light-blue lighten-4">
    <div class="section white z-depth-2">
      <div class="container flow-text">
        <h2 class="header">The Stave</h2>
        <p>Understanding extensions of the stave (Click each heading for a description)</p>
        <p>For Grade 2 you will need to know the two lines above and below the stave</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col s12">
      <ul class="tabs tabs-fixed-width z-depth-1">
        <li class="tab"><a class="active" href="#treble">Treble Clef</a></li>
        <li class="tab"><a href="#bass">Bass Clef</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="row container flow-text">

      <div class="col offset-s2">

        <div class="col s9">
          <p>Sometimes notes may go off of the provided lines and spaces of the stave.</p>
          <p>These notes are drawn with added lines to show their position.</p>
        </div>

        <div id="treble" class="col s12">
          <div class="col s11">
            <h3>Above The Stave</h3>
            <p>The notes shown above the stave are <b>G</b>, <b>A</b>, <b>B</b>, <b>C</b>, <b>D</b></p>
            <div class="stave">
              <div class="col s12 vex-tabdiv" width=400 scale=1.3>
                options space=20 font-size=12
                stave
                clef = treble
                notes :4 G-A-B/5 C-D/6
                text :4,.-1,G, A, B, C, D
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col s11">
            <h3>Below The Stave</h3>
            <p>The notes shown below the stave are <b>D</b>, <b>C</b>, <b>B</b>, <b>A</b>, <b>G</b></p>
            <div class="stave">
              <div class="col s12 vex-tabdiv" width=400 scale=1.3>
                options space=20 font-size=12
                stave
                clef = treble
                notes :4 D-C/4 B-A-G/3
                text :4, D, C, B, A, G
                options space=10
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="bass" class="col s12">
          <div class="col s11">
            <h3>Above The Stave</h3>
            <p>The notes shown above the stave are <b>B</b>, <b>C</b>, <b>D</b>, <b>E</b>, <b>F</b></p>
            <div class="stave">
              <div class="col s12 vex-tabdiv" width=400 scale=1.3>
                options space=20 font-size=12
                stave
                clef = bass
                notes :4 B/3 C-D-E-F/4
                text :4, .-1, B, C, D, E, F
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col s11">
            <h3>Below The Stave</h3>
            <p>The notes shown below the stave are <b>F</b>, <b>E</b>, <b>D</b>, <b>C</b>, <b>B</b></p>
            <div class="stave">
              <div class="col s12 vex-tabdiv" width=400 scale=1.3>
                options space=20 font-size=12
                stave
                clef = bass
                notes :4 F-E-D-C/2 B/1
                text :4, F, E, D, C, B
                options space=10
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </main>
  <% include ./include/scripts %>
  <% include ./include/footer %>
